A parcel of land (Lot M-2-A, of the subdivision plan (LRC) Psd ____, being a portion of Lot N-2, (LRC) Psd-107284, LRC Rec. No. ____ ), situated in the Barrio of Cadlan, municipality of Pili, Province of Camarines Sur, Island of Luzon, bounded on the N., along points 1 to 3 by Lot 1-B-2-C-1; on the NE., along points 3 to 16 by Lot N-1, (LRC) Psd-107284; on the SE., along points 16 to 24 by Pongel Creek; on the SW and NW., along points 24 to 1 by Lot M-2-B, of the subdivision plan (creek); Beginning a point marked “1” on plan being S.7 deg. 21’W., 1639.46 From MBM No. 1 Barrio Palestina, Pili, Camarines Sur;

